<a name="news"><font size="2"><font color="firebrick"><b><u>Latest News</u></b></font></font></a><br />
<ul><li><b>Default UI for Download:</b> The <a href="http://www.synex-flux.com/Other/defaultuifiles/index.html" target="_blank">Default UI Files</a> have been updated courtesy of <a href="http://www.mysticscrolls.com/EverQuest/index.asp" target="_blank">mysticscrolls.com</a>; both a zip package and the individual files are available.<br />
<br />
<li><b>New T.King address:</b> Per <a href="http://pub165.ezboard.com/fmaximus94788frm10.showMessage?topicID=74.topic" target="_blank">Thomus King</a>, all his home- and art-pages have changed from <font color="brown">attbi.com</font> to <b><font color="blue">comcast.net</font></b>; don't forget to update your bookmarks!<br />
<br />
